art center & festival

what does kentuck do?

Kentuck Art Center offers programs to support the arts, connect with the community, and help artists grow. Through a mix of free and paid activities like Art Nights, workshops, Boxes of Joy, and the Kentuck Festival of the Arts, we strive to make art accessible to everyone. We invite you to browse our Gallery Shop, register for your next favorite workshop, apply to exhibit your work at the Kentuck Festival, or visit us for an Art Market!

join our ken-folk

When you support Kentuck, you play a key role in building and sustaining a vibrant arts community that enriches the cultural fabric of West Alabama. Members get great perks, including complimentary beer or wine at Art Nights, discounts in the Gallery Shop, and discounts on workshops!
